	* tramp.texi (Predefined connection information): Revert previous
	change.

2018-12-10  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Quick Start Guide): New section "Using sudoedit".
	(External methods) <sudoedit>: Describe.
	(Predefined connection information): "session-timeout" is also for
	"sudoedit".

2018-12-09  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Ad-hoc multi-hops): Involved methods must be inline
	methods.

2018-11-24  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (External methods) <rclone>: Mention adding flags.

2018-11-22  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Top): Remove "History".
	(History): Remove node.
	(Quick Start Guide): New section "Using rclone".
	(External methods) <rclone>: Describe.

2018-11-21  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Inline methods) <sudo, doas>: Both methods expire
	the underlying session per default.
	(Predefined connection information): Explain "session-timeout".

2018-11-16  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Customizing Methods): Mention ELPA packages which
	add new methods to Tramp.

2018-11-08  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Password handling): Explain Ange FTP case.

2018-11-06  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Multi-hops): Exclude ports and domains from pattern
	expansion.

2018-10-31  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (File name completion): User and host name completion
	is also performed by auth-sources search.

2018-10-20  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Quick Start Guide): Improve wording.
	(Change file name syntax): Say, that `tramp-file-name-regexp' is
	not constant.
	(Ad-hoc multi-hops): Explain host name expansion.

2018-10-04  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* Makefile.in (../INSTALL): Add "--paragraph-indent=none" argument.

	* tramp.texi (Top, Bug Reports): Use `tramp-bug-report-address'.

	* trampinst.texi: Do not set `@paragraphindent'.
	(Suggestions): Use `tramp-bug-report-address'.

	* trampver.texi.in (tramp-bug-report-address): New variable.
	(trampfn): Change check for definition of macro.

2018-10-03  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* trampver.texi.in (trampfn): Call `unmacro' prior defining.
	trampver.texi is included several times; it raises an error
	otherwise.

2018-10-02  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* Makefile.in (PLAINTEXT_FILES): New variable.
	(.PHONY, all): Add target `plaintext'.
	(plaintext, ../INSTALL): New entries.

	* tramp.texi (trampfn): Moved to trampver.texi.in.
	(Top): Add sections `System Requirement' and `Basic Installation'.

	* trampinst.texi: Merged with ../INSTALL.  That file is generated
	from now on.
	(System Requirements, Basic Installation, Suggestions): New sections.
	(Load paths): Use Info-directory-list`.

	* trampver.texi.in (trampfn): New macro, taken from tramp.texi.

2018-10-01  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Password handling): Say "user option".
	(Remote shell setup): Say "environment variable".
	(External packages): Add `non-essential' to variable index.

