	Version 2.3.0 released.

2016-06-01  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (Password handling): Do not discuss anymore how
	to get password-cache.el.  It is bundled with Emacs.

2016-02-24  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* tramp.texi (File name completion): Do not use @trampfn{} for
	IPv6 addresses.  Somehow, it results in errors during PDF
	creation in the Emacs repository.

