2016-01-25  Michael Albinus  <michael.albinus@gmx.de>

	* .gitignore: Add *.pdf.

	* Makefile.in (EMACS_GVFS, tramp.dvi, tramp.html): Remove.
	(MAKEINFO): Move fixed parts into the variable.
	(.PHONY, all): Add pdf.
	($(INFO_FILES)): Shorten MAKEINFO call.
	(dvi html pdf): Combine rule.  Add pdf.

	* tramp.texi: Merge changes from Emacs repository, especially
	for @trampfn{}.
	(Top): Move @ifnottex down.
	(History): XEmacs support has been removed.
	(GVFS based methods, Remote processes): Do not use emacsgvfs flag.
	(Auto-save and Backup): Use both syntax versions.

	* trampinst.texi (Testing): Adapt @trampfn{} call.

	* trampver.texi.in: Do not set emacsgvfs flag.

