	unused flags and the enclosed alternative text for XEmacs.

	* trampver.texi.in: Rename "emacs" and "xemacs" flags to "unified"
	and "separate".  Remove flags "emacsname", "emacsdir",
	"ftppackagename", "emacsothername", "emacsotherdir" and
	"emacsotherfilename".

